Module it.polimi.ingsw.PSP18

Package it.polimi.ingsw.PSP18.server.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Cell
    This is the class that contains all the methods to manage the map's cells Every cell is identified by a building level (ranging from 0 to 3), a worker reference and a flag if a dome is present
    GameMap
    This is the class that contains all the methods to manage the game map A map is a 5x5 array of cells and stores the last action information for updating gui and differential update
    Move
    Stores a move direction and level difference A move is identified by one of eight possible direction and a differential change in level
    PlayerData
    Stores the data of the player and its state A player has an unique id, color and a divinity assigned
    Worker
    Stores the worker coordinates and the player that owns the worker details
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Color
    This is the class that contains all the possible colors for the player
    Direction
    This is the class that contains all the possible moves directions Every direction has a string that represents its value for cli management
    MatchStatus
    Used to determine the match status
